      <title>安装使用zsh及其强大的插件</title>
      <link>https://blog.00002000.xyz/post/code/linux/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8zsh%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%BC%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</link>
